---
title: One-Pan Tomato & Bean Skillet Italiano With Zucchini, Ricotta & Parmesan Croutons
description: Love the flavors of pizza? Of course, you do, you’re only human! That’s why our chefs channeled our favorite late-night bite into a one-pan dinner that’s packed with veggies and protein. Zucchini and cannellini beans simmer with diced tomatoes for the saucy component. That’s dolloped with creamy, mild ricotta cheese. Then say hello to big and crunchy croutons. They cover the top with some Parmesan, which becomes all melty when popped into the oven. Where has this skillet bean all our lives??
